'''布格塞拉國際機場'''（{{lang-en|Bugesera International Airport}}，{{Airport codes|暫無|暫無}}）為位於[[盧旺達|盧旺達]]的一座興建中的[[機場|機場]]。<ref name="Start">{{cite web |accessdate=14 August 2017 |url=https://www.theeastafrican.co.ke/rwanda/Business/Construction-work-on-Bugesera-Airport-starts-/1433224-4056862-gys2md/index.html |title=Construction work on Bugesera Airport starts |date=2017-08-14 |newspaper=The EastAfrican |first=Rodrigues |last=Rwirahira |location=Nairobi |archive-date=2019-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191106024446/https://www.theeastafrican.co.ke/rwanda/Business/Construction-work-on-Bugesera-Airport-starts-/1433224-4056862-gys2md/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|date=2014-07-16|accessdate=2016-09-07|url=http://allafrica.com/stories/201407170161.html|title=Rwanda: Bugesera Airport Project To Start After Families' Pay-Off|newspaper=New Times (Rwanda) via AllAfrica.com|last=Habimana|first=Seraphine|location=Kigali|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304095621/http://allafrica.com/stories/201407170161.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="On">{{cite web |title=Bugesera construction at 10pc, five months on |access-date=2018-02-05 |first=Ivan |last=Mugisha |url=https://www.theeastafrican.co.ke/rwanda/Business/Bugesera-construction-five-months-on/1433224-4289358-u5qcmy/index.html |date=2018-02-04 |newspaper=The EastAfrican |location=Nairobi |archive-date=2019-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191106024429/https://www.theeastafrican.co.ke/rwanda/Business/Bugesera-construction-five-months-on/1433224-4289358-u5qcmy/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 地理位置 ==
布格塞拉機場座落於盧旺達東南部的[[布格塞拉縣|布格塞拉縣]]，海拔高度約為1,400公尺<ref>{{cite web | title=Elevation of Rilima Above Sea Level | author=FRC | url=http://www.fallingrain.com/world/RW/11/Rilima.html | date=2017-08-17 | accessdate=2017-08-17 | publisher=Fallingrain.com  (FRC) | archive-date=2018-06-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613020002/http://www.fallingrain.com/world/RW/11/Rilima.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>，鄰近[[里利馬|里利馬]]。<ref name="Where">{{cite web |url=http://allafrica.com/stories/201708110118.html |title=Rwanda:Bugesera Residents Eye Jobs as Works on New Airport Take Off |date=2017-08-11 |accessdate=2017-08-17 |last=Mwai |first=Collins |newspaper=New Times (Rwanda) |location=Kigali |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170818045213/http://allafrica.com/stories/201708110118.html |archive-date=2017-08-18 }}</ref>該機場位於[[基加利國際機場|基加利國際機場]]以南，兩者直線距離約25公里，車程則約40公里。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://distancecalculator.globefeed.com/Rwanda_Distance_Result.asp?fromplace=Kigali%20International%20Airport%2C%20KN%205%20Road%2C%20Kigali%2C%20Rwanda&toplace=Rilima%2C%20Eastern%20Province%2C%20Rwanda%2C&dt1=ChIJ1XpB-Zan3BkR4v5rKXK660U&dt2=ChIJDxFNfQyrxBkRZ3PWePix2Vg |accessdate=2017-08-17 |title=Distance between Kigali International Airport, KN 5 Road, Kigali, Rwanda and Rilima, Eastern Province, Rwanda |publisher=Globefeed.com (GFC) |author=GFC |date=2017-08-17 |archive-date=2018-09-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180902183901/https://distancecalculator.globefeed.com/Rwanda_Distance_Result.asp?fromplace=Kigali%20International%20Airport%2C%20KN%205%20Road%2C%20Kigali%2C%20Rwanda&toplace=Rilima%2C%20Eastern%20Province%2C%20Rwanda%2C&dt1=ChIJ1XpB-Zan3BkR4v5rKXK660U&dt2=ChIJDxFNfQyrxBkRZ3PWePix2Vg |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 概要 ==
布格塞拉機場完工之後將成為盧旺達境內最大的國際機場，也將是該國第八座機場以及第三座國際機場。該機場將為來往大基加利都會區的民用航班提供服務。<ref name="One">{{cite web|accessdate=2014-11-29|url=http://expogr.com/detail_news.php?newsid=107&pageid=2&t=New%20Bugesera%20International%20Airport,%20Rwanda%20among%20projects%20that%20need%20US$1bn|title=New Bugesera International Airport, Rwanda Among Projects That Need US$1 Billion|date=2014-08-13|author=EXPOGR|publisher=Expogr.Com (EXPOGR) Quoting Construction Review Online|archive-date=2020-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201019173422/https://expogr.com/detail_news.php?newsid=107&pageid=2&t=New%20Bugesera%20International%20Airport,%20Rwanda%20among%20projects%20that%20need%20US$1bn|dead-url=no}}</ref>由於基加利國際機場的客運量已達該機場的設計容量上限，布格塞拉機場一旦完工將能有效分擔基加利機場的航班。<ref name="On"/><ref name="One"/>

布格塞拉機場的第一期工程將只會興建一條[[跑道|跑道]]，待第二期工程完工後，第二條跑道才會投入使用。第一期工程的預算估計為4.18億美元，第二期則是3.82億美元，兩者總計8億美元。第一期工程原計畫於2018年<ref name="Ink">{{cite web | date=2016-09-02 | url=https://www.theeastafrican.co.ke/business/Rwanda-inks-deal-with-Portuguese-firm-for-Bugesera-airport/2560-3367362-yky73m/index.html | title=Rwanda inks $418m deal with Portuguese firm for Bugesera airport | newspaper=The East African | location=Nairobi | author=Ivan R. Mugisha | accessdate=2016-09-07 | archive-date=2018-06-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613015153/http://www.theeastafrican.co.ke/business/Rwanda-inks-deal-with-Portuguese-firm-for-Bugesera-airport/2560-3367362-yky73m/index.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>或2019年<ref name="Start"/><ref name="On"/><ref name="Where"/>完工。新機場在規劃的過程中，英國的TPS工程顧問負責進行可行性評估和機場的整體設計。後期工程將同時提高機場的客運與貨運的容量。2010年11月，有報導指出盧旺達政府已聘請跨國會計師事務所[[普華永道|普華永道]]擔任機場新建工程的財務顧問，普華永道也將為該工程尋找資金來源。按照政府的計劃，機場的新建工程將採取[[政府和社會資本合作|民間參與公共建設]]模式。<ref name="On"/><ref>{{cite web |newspaper=The Independent (Uganda) |access-date=2018-02-05 |url=https://www.independent.co.ug/new-bugesera-international-airport-change-rwanda/ |title=New Bugesera International Airport Could Change Rwanda |date=2010-11-23 |location=Kampala |first=Esiara |last=Kabona |archive-date=2021-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120132343/https://www.independent.co.ug/new-bugesera-international-airport-change-rwanda/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2019年12月，[[卡塔爾航空|卡塔爾航空]]同意收購布格塞拉機場60%的股份。根據[[盧旺達發展局|盧旺達發展局]]的規劃，新機場第一期工程完工後將能服務每年700萬人次的旅客容量，第二期工程則預計2032年完工，屆時旅客容量將倍增至每年1400萬人次。<ref>{{cite web |date=2019-12-10 |url=https://www.aljazeera.com/ajimpact/qatar-airways-buy-rwandan-international-airport-191209212841510.html |title=Qatar Airways to buy new Rwandan international airport |publisher=Al Jazeera |access-date=2019-12-10 |archive-date=2020-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806154503/https://www.aljazeera.com/ajimpact/qatar-airways-buy-rwandan-international-airport-191209212841510.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.theeastafrican.co.ke/business/Qatar-Airways-stake-in-Rwanda-airport/2560-5379966-32mpxmz/index.html |title=Qatar Airways To Take Majority Stake In New Rwandan International Airport |newspaper=The EastAfrican |date=2019-12-10 |access-date=2019-12-10 |author=Reuters |archive-date=2020-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201011230107/https://www.theeastafrican.co.ke/business/Qatar-Airways-stake-in-Rwanda-airport/2560-5379966-32mpxmz/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 興建工程 ==
2016年9月，盧旺達政府和[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]]建築公司[[莫塔－英吉爾|莫塔－英吉爾]]正式簽約，機場將由該公司負責籌款、興建與營運，特許期限為25年，並可續約15年，莫塔－英吉爾公司並同意為第一期工程提供4.18億美元的資金。按原計畫，機場預定於2018年起正式提供民航服務。<ref name="Ink"/>

2017年8月，機場的興建工程正式展開，如今的預算已追加至8.28億美元。作為主要承包商，莫塔－英吉爾透過其子公司莫塔英吉爾非洲為興建工程提供75%的資金，剩餘的25%由盧旺達公司航空旅行與物流承擔，後者也將於機場開始營運後提供地勤服務。因變更設計，機場暫時停工，導致完工日期延後。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/bugesera-international-airport-under-redesign |title=Bugesera International Airport under redesign |publisher=New Times (Rwanda) |author=New Times Reporter |date=2019-04 |access-date=2019-04-10 |place=Kigali |archive-date=2019-03-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190320130037/https://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/bugesera-international-airport-under-redesign |dead-url=no }}</ref>

根據和卡塔爾航空合作後的新方案，機場的規模相比原計畫大幅擴大，工程預算也將提高至13.1億美元。新方案第一期工程的工期預計為5年，第二期工程則預計2032年完工。<ref name="LargeR">{{cite web |newspaper=Business Daily Africa |url=https://www.businessdailyafrica.com/corporate/companies/Qatar-Sh131bn-Rwanda-airport-set-to-rival-JKIA/4003102-5381184-yv1agsz/index.html |title=Qatar’s Sh131bn Rwanda airport set to rival JKIA |date=2019-12-11 |access-date=2019-12-11 |author=Gerald Andae |location=Nairobi |archive-date=2020-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813120454/https://www.businessdailyafrica.com/corporate/companies/Qatar-Sh131bn-Rwanda-airport-set-to-rival-JKIA/4003102-5381184-yv1agsz/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 規劃設施 ==
根據TPS工程顧問公司的報告，新機場的第一期工程完工後將能服務每年700萬人次的旅客運量，以及每年150萬公噸的貨運量。新機場將建有一座總樓地板面積約為30,000平方公尺的旅客航廈，該航廈將設有22座報到櫃台以及6座[[空橋|登機空橋]]。後續工程還計畫興建第二條跑道。<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.archdaily.com/911624/rwandas-bugesera-international-airport-to-set-records-for-sustainability | title=Rwanda’s Bugesera International Airport to Set Records for Sustainability | date=2019-02-20 | website=ArchDaily | access-date=2019-04-10 | archive-date=2021-01-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126132408/https://www.archdaily.com/911624/rwandas-bugesera-international-airport-to-set-records-for-sustainability | dead-url=no }}</ref>

